title: #167: Swing and a Miss (@Attell, @BigJayOakerson, @KurtMetzger)
itunes:title: Swing and a Miss with Dave Attell, Big Jay Oakerson, Kurt Metzger
description: Dave Attell joined Kurt Metzger, Big Jay Oakerson, and me at a table in front of the Stand comedy club in New York to talk. Talk about what? Not any single topic like this podcast is supposed to be. It was all meandering. From NYC bums, to Donald Sterling, to Dave's standup series Comedy Underground.
